ss=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">sean vagabundos, que desconf&iacute;en de </span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4716\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">los bancos, o que,</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">simplemente ca</span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4718\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">rezcan</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">de</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">habilidades</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">sociales.</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Tu </span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4719\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">clase social depender&aacute; de tus puntos </span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4720\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">de</span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4721\" class=\"markedContent\"> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Cr&eacute;dito</span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4722\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">, tal y como se indica a </span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4723\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">continuaci&oacute;n:</span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page155R_mcid4724\" class=\"markedContent\"><br role=\"presentation\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Cr&eacute;dito</span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4725\" class=\"markedContent\"> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">funciona de un modo dis</span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4727\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">tinto al resto de habilidades. Su va</span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4729\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">lor de puntuaci&oacute;n es a la vez una </span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4730\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">descripci&oacute;n del tipo de cr&eacute;dito que </span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4731\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">se posee y de la cantidad de puntos </span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4732\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">de</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">la</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">reserva.</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Se</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">puede</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">entender </span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4733\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">como ocho habilidades en una: Cr&eacute;</span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4735\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">dito (Clase baja), Cr&eacute;dito (Clase tra</span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4737\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">bajadora), Cr&eacute;dito (Clase media-al</span></span><span id=\"page155R_mcid4739\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">ta), etc. Sigue siendo una reserva <span id=\"page159R_mcid4863\" class=\"markedContent\">porque, sinceramente, en los a&ntilde;os </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4864\" class=\"markedContent\">30 especialmente, cuanto m&aacute;s alta </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4865\" class=\"markedContent\">era tu clase social, m&aacute;s oportunida</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4867\" class=\"markedContent\">des te brindaba la sociedad. En otras </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4868\" class=\"markedContent\">palabras: por lo normal, tus recur</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4870\" class=\"markedContent\">sos sociales aumentan junto a tu </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4871\" class=\"markedContent\">clase y riqueza.</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page155R_mcid4739\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><span id=\"page159R_mcid4872\" class=\"markedContent\"><br role=\"presentation\">Los aspectos sociales de</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4873\" class=\"markedContent\"> Cr&eacute;dito</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4874\" class=\"markedContent\"> pue</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4876\" class=\"markedContent\">den moverse entre uno o dos rangos </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4877\" class=\"markedContent\">si el Guardi&aacute;n cree que es plausible; </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4878\" class=\"markedContent\">un m&eacute;dico con</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4879\" class=\"markedContent\"> Cr&eacute;dito</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4880\" class=\"markedContent\"> 5 es posible </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4881\" class=\"markedContent\">que tratara con un electricista de cla</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4883\" class=\"markedContent\">se media o un especialista de clase </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4884\" class=\"markedContent\">alta y les pudiera pedir favores. </span></span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"page155R_mcid4739\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><span id=\"page159R_mcid4885\" class=\"markedContent\">Cr&eacute;dito</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4886\" class=\"markedContent\"> no describe necesariamen</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4888\" class=\"markedContent\">te el tama&ntilde;o de tu cuenta de aho<span id=\"page159R_mcid4836\" class=\"markedContent\">rros, sino tu capacidad de operar </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4837\" class=\"markedContent\">dentro de un sector socioecon&oacute;mi</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4839\" class=\"markedContent\">co determinado. Puedes llegar al </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4840\" class=\"markedContent\">nivel de</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4841\" class=\"markedContent\"> Cr&eacute;dito</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4842\" class=\"markedContent\"> que quieres, cas&aacute;n</span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4844\" class=\"markedContent\">dote, heredando, o bien teniendo </span><span id=\"page159R_mcid4845\" class=\"markedContent\">parientes haciendo amigos